<view>
  <view>
    <text class="txt3">{{current==0?"农作物病害名称":"害虫类型最接近"}}：{{name}}</text>
    <text class="txt2" w>根据模型为您筛选出{{real?1:0}} 中结果可能</text>

    <swiper wx:if="{{real}}" style="height:300rpx" current="{{select}}" duration="300" bindchange="activeSw" next-margin="40rpx">
      <swiper-item wx:for="{{1}}" data-id="{{item}}" wx:key="index" bindtap="goto">
        <view>
          <view class="items">
            <view wx:if="{{index==0}}" class="item">
              <image src="{{data.img}}" />
              <view class="right">
                <text class="a">{{data.ch_name}}</text>
                <text class="b">相似度：{{tensor}}%</text>
              </view>
            </view>
            <view wx:else class="item">
              <image src="{{item.img[0]}}" />
              <view class="right">
                <text class="a">{{item.ch_name}}</text>
                <text class="b">相似度：40%</text>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </swiper-item>
    </swiper>

    <view class="real" wx:if="{{!real}}">
      <text>未检测到相关目标，建议您重新上传图片识别</text>
    </view>

  </view>
  <view class="txt1">用时：<text style=" color: rgb(144, 231, 103);">{{time/1000}}</text>秒</view>
  <view class="a">
    <button class="btn_1" role="button" bindtap="collect">
      <text class="txt">收藏</text>
    </button>
    <button class="btn_2" role="button" bindtap="chooseimage" open-type="share" plain id="appShare">
      <text class="txt">分享</text>
    </button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{!next}}" class="waring">
  <image src="/images/waring.png" />
  <text>该功能为我们自己使用卷积神经网络训练而成,识别结果依赖于训练权重，信息仅供参考</text>
</view>

</view>